{"title":"住手，疯狂的海盗","authors":["顾工"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":8,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"住手，疯狂的海盗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顾工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国炮弹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在红河口外，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轰轰爆炸；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国飞机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在越南上空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爆裂火花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"约翰逊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想用“东京湾”的迷雾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"编织一个欺骗世界的神话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"趁机把战火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扩大，扩大，扩大！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泰勒——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“肯尼迪的灵魂”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“美国第一流军事专家”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在朝鲜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丢盔曳甲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊魂未定，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又妄想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用“战略村”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扼死印度支那；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用“特种战争”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"征服东南亚；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用白宫的令箭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驱赶一批"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃人肉的禽兽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃心肝的豺狼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越过一条条经纬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越过一道道国界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥舞五角大楼的战刀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处大砍大杀……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"住手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"疯狂的海盗；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"止步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华尔街的爪牙！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们可还记得上甘岭？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们可还知道奠边府？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们可还想到你们在南越"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被拔除的军事哨所？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被歼灭的凶恶人马？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"住手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"疯狂的海盗；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"止步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华尔街的爪牙！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你敢向"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越南民主共和国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不停止侵犯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国六亿五千万人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就要和全世界人民一起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同你斗争到底，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把你的魔爪砍下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"住手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"疯狂的海盗；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"止步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华尔街的爪牙！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的飞机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在越南上空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"栽下一架，一架又一架……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——多好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是英雄战士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发出的庄严警告；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——多美，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是革命人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庆祝胜利的礼花！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国飞机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在越南上空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纷纷爆裂；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国海盗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在南越地面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纷纷倒下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"死神，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正在叩打，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白宫的大门；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"墓碑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在五角大楼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开始安插；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帝国主义的丧钟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正在全世界敲响。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看，蓝天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看，四海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪射出千道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命胜利的金光；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞舞起万朵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义的红霞！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}